Package: CoexprArabidopsis
Title: Extended Gene Coexpression Analysis Pipeline
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Tatsuya", "Nobori", , "tatsuyanobori@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Takes any preprocessed 10x single-cell/single-nucleus dataset
    (currently Seurat objects) and produces context-robust co-expression modules
    with biological interpretation, plus a gene-of-interest (GOI) lookup resource.
    Supports two first-class estimation modes (pseudobulk and SingleCellGGM) with
    an optional cross-context robustness layer.
